snippet.title: EveryName Secret Boss Fight | RIBBIT [ DELTARUNE MOD ]
snippet.description:
This is one of the most amazing fan-made undertale / deltarune fights i have ever played (this fight replaces the jevil secret boss fight)
Get the game here! (you need the original 2018 version of deltarune chapter 1) :
https://gamejolt.com/games/ribbitmod/671888
Creator:
https://twitter.com/BeholdMaxine
another ribbit video:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eYl1srylw-A
(The Deltarune Survey Program download link is on the Ribbit Mod text file)
